     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       As w tlkd bt n th Tr Cst f Stff, byng smthng nw rqrs th xtrctn nd dstrctn f  lt f rsrcs, nt t mntn th dstrctn f r nvrnmnt n xtrctng, hlng, mnfctrng, pckgng nd shppng th tm.
      </p>
      <p>
       S f w wnt t vd byng nw thngs, wht shld w d f w nd smthng? Aftr ll, thr r lwys tms whn w fl w nd smthng — nt jst wnt r dsr, bt nd t fr  rl prps. W mght nd nw clths, r bks, r  bk s w cn ct bck n sng  cr.
      </p>
      <p>
       On wmn dcdd t
       <a href="http://thenonconsumeradvocate.wordpress.com/exceptions-to-katys-compact-buy-nothing-new/">
        by nthng nw
       </a>
       , whch s n ntrstng sltn, bt prbbly nt fr mst ppl. Bt whl y mght nt wnt t pt sch  drstc mrtrm n yrslf, hr r 7 thngs y cn d bfr vn cnsdrng byng  nw tm.
      </p>
      <ol>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Rcnsdr yr nd
        </strong>
        . D y rlly rlly nd t? Or s t  wnt? Or cn y chng thngs s y dn’t nd t? Ths shld lwys b th frst thng y d.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Brrw
        </strong>
        . Y mght nly nd t tmprrly. Brrw bks frm frnds r th lbrry. Brrw  drss fr  spcl ccsn. Brrw  tl fr  shrt-trm prjct. B sr t lnd thngs n rtrn, whn y cn.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Ask frnds nd fmly
        </strong>
        . Smtms ppl y knw mght hv th tm y nd, bt nt nd t ny lngr. Instd f lnng t t y, thy mght b gld t gv t t y. Y nly nd t sk. I’ll ftn snd t n ml (r twt) f I nd smthng tht thrs mght hv.
       </li>
       <li>
        <a href="http://freecycle.org">
         <strong>
          Frcycl
         </strong>
        </a>
        . Sm d, bt sng  wdr ntwrk. Thr r Frcycl ntwrks n mny rs — ppl wh wnt t gv smthng wy, r wh nd smthng, pst t th lst nd vry ftn xchngs r md — fr fr.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         By sd
        </strong>
        . It’s nfntly bttr thn byng nw, bcs whn y by sd y’r nt hvng nw rsrcs tkn frm th rth nd mnfctrd, bt rthr xtndng th lf f rsrcs tht hv lrdy bn sd. Try thrft shps, chrty strs, yrd r grg sls,
        <a href="http://craigslist.org">
         Crgslst
        </a>
        r
        <a href="http://ebay.com">
         Eby
        </a>
        .
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Mk yr wn
        </strong>
        . Ths wn’t wrk n vry cs (f I hd t mk my wn clths ppl wld lgh t m mr thn thy lrdy d), bt smtms y cn mk smthng tht’s jst s gd s byng, wth nxpnsv mtrls r mtrls y lrdy hv. Ths wrks f y’r gd wth crfts r crpntry spclly. It cn ls b fn t gt th fmly nvlvd.
       </li>
