        <strong>
         rght nw
        </strong>
        . Oftn thngs wll trn p whn y kp yr ys pn — smn wll hppn t mntn thy hv th tm, r y’ll s t n Frcycl r Crgslst ftr  wk r tw. And smtms, th nd fr th tm wll g wy, nd y’ll b gld y wtd.
